{"tid":1899381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[財政預算] 政府撤回3間大學醫療教學設施撥款，警隊開支預算大增至258億","createTime":"2020-02-26T14:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T04:29:10.000Z","uid":127929,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c771906a8435cdec02918ef7772ed78167d82e97","tid":1899381,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:31:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應該投資既教育：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2019.11.15【抗暴之戰】突抽走14億擴建理大撥款申請 政府被批打壓高教發展</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Af2PxL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAf2PxL0.jpg&h=ff47b461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2019-11-29政府第三度抽起大學工程撥款 涉中大港大 2.5 億醫療教學設施撥款</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RseqQvh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRseqQvh.png&h=b044d9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2019-11-29 政府撤回大學醫療教學設施撥款 消息：幾乎全體建制派突改不支持</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zy7oB7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzy7oB7C.jpg&h=8417a997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">浪費資源淨係識打市民既黑社會：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2020-02-26 預算案】申8,000萬換6裝甲車 警隊開支預算258億幾近8紀律部隊總和<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhRMz2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhRMz2B.png&h=b20629c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲未計抗疫基金同黑警加薪,同冇生産力既廢老生果金新移民綜緩出雙糧 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">應該洗錢既就扣起，多餘冇用既就不停注資，洗亂咁洗錢既垃圾政府係咪痴撚線架！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n想要收個1萬蚊就先要支持政府咁撚樣亂鳩fing納稅人既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f